com.kuka.geometry

Class FrameChainElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kuka.geometry.FrameChainElement

  • public final class FrameChainElement
extends Object
    A single frame chain element in the directed path from source to target frame. Each element in a FrameChain knows its neighboring elements including the connections to the direct neighbors. All frame chain elements are immutable.

      • isConnectionToNextFrameInverted

        public boolean isConnectionToNextFrameInverted()
